properties.description: Situated in the serene setting of Via Molina 36 in Vallemosso, this townhouse represents the perfect balance between local architectural tradition and the comforts of modern living. Recently partially renovated, the home welcomes visitors with a living area designed for conviviality and relaxation. Upon entering the ground floor, you're immediately struck by the functionality of the spaces: a spacious eat-in kitchen sits alongside a cozy living room, creating a warm and inviting home environment. Making this property unique is the presence of a quaint rumpus room, an ideal spot for dinners
